title: Tom Brady's suspension reaction
itunes:title: Tom Brady's suspension reaction
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- react to Tom Brady's 4-game suspension discussing the severity, Jimmy Garoppolo, and much more.
